desc: Limited edition Street Art, Designer Toys and Movie Prints from artists like Mr. Brainwash, Hebru Brantley, Kaws and more! Multitude Gallery is an art store in Chicago, Illinois specializing in unique paintings and screen prints.

layout.text: Multitude Gallery is your premier destination for street, urban and graffiti art.  Shop our wide selection of artists including Mr. Brainwash, Shepard Fairey, Hebru Brantley, Cleon Peterson and more!
